{"tid":51311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"變態鬧洞房　眾男「多P」對新娘摸奶看下體","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T06:00:37.000Z","uid":19707,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6217528ba1be068bcb5e34b81c87ef2666cd9072","tid":51311,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"中國又出現變態低俗婚禮，一段流傳在《秒拍》平台的影片上看到，有一群男子闖入新房內，對著幾乎是全裸的新娘「多P」亂摸。<br />\n<br />\n影片中只見新娘僅用一條薄薄的棉被遮住上半身，但下半身幾乎是完全裸露，但一群男子不斷對新娘襲胸，鏡頭也直接拍到新娘的「鮑魚」，其畫面比A片更猥褻。就有網友批評這群男子「根本是一群野獸」，還有網友形容「你確定這不是一群喪屍？」。英國《每日郵報》也指出，這則短短10秒的影片上傳秒拍之後，2天內就吸引超過170萬次的點閱率。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161223/1018847/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161223%2F1018847%2F%23&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YveZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2754ba48\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161223/1018847/#</a>"},{"pid":"5947316c20e8a8d2399de6016770abac252264d6","tid":51311,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"支那文化"},{"pid":"7f257a83c1448a4ea00a8bc06cf2fdc6372d9d87","tid":51311,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"咩地方習俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ac7f107b4bb57bdf135ccad75c376bd9b29c23","tid":51311,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02851f852aad01672de7487bbb446954d7268315","tid":51311,"uid":19436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"咁大件衫點樣幾乎全裸"},{"pid":"5029b040316a72f96a0